## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-102">这`enum`事件发生时指定的事件类型<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-102">This `enum` specifies the event type when an event is raised for an <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-103">修改 XML 树的所有操作都细分为一系列基元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-103">All operations that modify the XML tree break down to a series of primitives.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9186-104">有四种类型的基元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-104">There are four types of primitives.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9186-105">两个基元 （添加和删除） 操作集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-105">Two of the primitives (Add and Remove) act on collections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9186-106">其中 （名称和值） 的两个实例上执行的操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-106">Two of them (Name and Value) act on instances.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9186-107">没有为每个这些基元对应的事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-107">There is a corresponding event for each of these primitives.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-108">修改 XML 树中的这些事件，因为执行此操作可能导致意外结果时，你应当小心。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-108">You should be careful when modifying an XML tree within one of these events, because doing this might lead to unexpected results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9186-109">例如，如果你收到<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing>事件，并且在处理该事件时从树中删除节点，则您可能不会收到<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-109">For example, if you receive a <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing> event, and while the event is being processed you remove the node from the tree, you might not receive the <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9186-110">处理事件时，它是有效地修改 XML 树而非在包含在接收事件; 的节点是修改同一个树，修改不影响在其引发事件的特定节点提供更有效。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-110">When an event is being processed, it is valid to modify an XML tree other than the one that contains the node that is receiving the event; it is even valid to modify the same tree provided the modifications do not affect the specific nodes on which the event was raised.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9186-111">但是，如果你修改包含接收事件的节点的区域，那么你收到的事件和到树的影响是树的不确定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-111">However, if you modify the area of the tree that contains the node receiving the event, the events that you receive and the impact to the tree are undefined.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-112">下面的示例通过将元素添加到树中引发事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-112">The following example raises an event by adding an element to the tree.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root", "content");  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Add(new XElement("Child", "child content"));  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-113">该示例产生下面的输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-113">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Add  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Add  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-114">下面的示例通过从树中移除一个元素而引发事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-114">The following example raises an event by removing an element from the tree.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root",  
    new XElement("Child", "content")  
);  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Element("Child").Remove();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-115">该示例产生下面的输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-115">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Remove  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Remove  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-116">下面的示例引发事件，通过更改元素的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-116">The following example raises an event by changing the name of an element.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root", "content");  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Name = "NewName";  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-117">该示例产生下面的输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-117">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changing: Name  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XElement  
  Changed: Name  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-118">下面的示例引发事件，通过设置属性的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-118">The following example raises an event by setting the value of an attribute.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XElement root = new XElement("Root",  
    new XAttribute("Att", "att value")  
);  
root.Changing += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changing event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changing: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.Changed += (sender, e) =>  
    {  
        Console.WriteLine("Changed event raised");  
        Console.WriteLine("  Sender: " + sender.GetType());  
        Console.WriteLine("  Changed: " + e.ObjectChange);  
    };  
root.FirstAttribute.Value = "new contents";  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9186-119">该示例产生下面的输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9186-119">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
Changing event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XAttribute  
  Changing: Value  
Changed event raised  
  Sender: System.Xml.Linq.XAttribute  
  Changed: Value  
```
